_sText:
Suppost to be a small fix 4 months ago, Now its is a whole remake of the map ze_jurassicpark_v2_1_ob made by wesker.
The map is 89mb when unpacked but it is 30 mb once it is bzipped.
It has 7 minutes of game play and is recommended to have each round at 9 or 10 mins.
The map time should be around 30 mins to get atleast 4-5 rounds in.
